(98, 'Northern Lights Observation Protocols', 'The study outlines a comprehensive methodology for capturing and analyzing auroral phenomena occurring in the polar sky. Utilizing enchanted instruments, this document details the calibration, data collection, and interpretative strategies necessary to decode the mysteries of the ethereal lights that dance above.'),
