(274, 'Candy Cane Lane Road Design', 'This report outlines the whimsical design specifications for Candy Cane Lane, envisioned to enhance sleigh navigation during festive rush hours. Utilizing bioluminescent sugar crystals as road markings, this innovative layout will guide travelers through enchanted snowdrifts with sugary illumination.'),
