(279, 'Mrs. Claus''s Enchanted Recipe Enhancement', 'In a daring attempt to enhance the classic gingerbread formula, we’ve infused an ancient spice that resonates with warmth and joy. Preliminary taste tests indicate a delightful aroma that seems to linger in the air, enchanting all who dare to sample this festive delight.'),
