(282, 'Reindeer Housing Innovations', 'This document outlines the advanced concepts in reindeer habitation, focusing on maximizing comfort and energy efficiency. Notably, the integration of insulated walls and bioluminescent lighting aims to create a serene environment while enhancing the reindeers'' natural behaviors during the long, frosty nights.'),
